"title": "8774: legalism",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8774",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The belief that salvation demands or depends upon total obedience to the letter of the law. Examples of legalism include an excessive concern for minute details of the law coupled with a neglect of its funadmental concerns, and a preoccupation with human legal traditions.</p>\n<h2>Legalism represents a fatal misunderstanding of the purpose of OT law</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom9:31-Rom9:32\">ROM 9:31–9:32</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom3:20\">ROM 3:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal3:10-Gal3:11\">GAL 3:10–3:11</a></p>\n<h2>Legalism is contrary to the gospel</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal2:16\">GAL 2:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt23:13\">MAT 23:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt23:15\">MAT 23:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom3:20-Rom3:24\">ROM 3:20–3:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil3:8-Phil3:9\">PHP 3:8–3:9</a></p>\n<h2>Paul:  example of a Jewish legalist</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil3:4-Phil3:6\">PHP 3:4–3:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal1:14\">GAL 1:14</a></p>\n<h2>The ugly effects of legalism</h2>\n<h3>Lack of love</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt23:23\">MAT 23:23</a></strong> <em>Legalism actually contradicts the spirit of OT law.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos6:6\">HOS 6:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic6:7-Mic6:8\">MIC 6:7–6:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt23:14\">MAT 23:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:31-Luke10:32\">LUK 10:31–10:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John7:49\">JHN 7:49</a></p>\n<h3>Spiritual pride</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:11-Luke18:12\">LUK 18:11–18:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:1-Matt6:2\">MAT 6:1–6:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:5\">MAT 6:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:16\">MAT 6:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt23:5-Matt23:7\">MAT 23:5–23:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke16:15\">LUK 16:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom10:3\">ROM 10:3</a></p>\n<h3>Formalism</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa29:13\">ISA 29:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark7:6\">MRK 7:6</a></p>\n<h3>Degeneration into man-made rules</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa29:13\">ISA 29:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark7:7-Mark7:8\">MRK 7:7–7:8</a></p>\n<h3>Hypocrisy</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt23:27-Matt23:28\">MAT 23:27–23:28</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam15:19-1Sam15:22\">1SA 15:19–15:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt15:3-Matt15:9\">MAT 15:3–15:9</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark7:9-Mark7:13\">MRK 7:9–7:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt23:25-Matt23:26\">MAT 23:25–23:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John7:19\">JHN 7:19</a></p>\n<h3>Spiritual blindness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John9:16\">JHN 9:16</a></strong></p>\n<h2>Warnings against legalism</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:6\">MAT 16:6</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark8:15\">MRK 8:15</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:12\">MAT 16:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal4:10-Gal4:11\">GAL 4:10–4:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:2-Gal5:4\">GAL 5:2–5:4</a></p>\n<h2>The burden of legalism</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts15:10\">ACT 15:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps130:3\">PSA 130:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas2:10\">JAS 2:10</a></p>\n<h2>The answer to legalism: the grace of Jesus Christ</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts15:11\">ACT 15:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:17\">MAT 5:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal3:13\">GAL 3:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal4:21-Gal4:31\">GAL 4:21–4:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:8-Eph2:9\">EPH 2:8–2:9</a></p>",
